rucción residencial, especialistas enseguridad y trabajadores. Los nuevos usuarios de pistolas de clavos deben recibir instrucción en seguridad, no solamente una copia de esta publicación. Los requisitos para la instrucción en seguridad están descritos en detalle en Nail Gun Safety: A Guide for Construction Contractors y pueden ser vistos o impresos o descargados de www.cdc.gov/spanish/niosh/docs/2011-202_sp.  aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (NIOSH, viewed April 22, 2019). 0aAccidentsxPrevention.0https://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh85000371 0aConstruction industry.0https://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh85031360 0aConstruction workers.0https://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh85031450 0aPneumatic nailers.0https://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh00009362 0aSafety education.0https://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh85116442 2aAccidents, Occupationalxprevention & control.0https://id.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/D000062Q000517 2aConstruction Industry.0https://id.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/D060389 2aSafety Management.0https://id.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/D017751 7aAccidentsxPrevention.2fast0(OCoLC)fst00795276 7aConstruction industry.2fast0(OCoLC)fst00875964 7aConstruction workers.2fast0(OCoLC)fst00876155 7aPneumatic nailers.2fast0(OCoLC)fst01067538 7aSafety education.2fast0(OCoLC)fst011033452 aNational Institute for Occupational Safety and Health,eissuing body.0https://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n7906315608iEnglish version:tStraight talk about nail gun safetyw(OCoLC)109803481108iPrint version:tPlática directa sobre seguridad con pistolas de clavosw(OCoLC)846836880 0aDHHS publication ;vno. (NIOSH) 2013-149 (Sp2013)0https://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n4203738640uhttps://purl.fdlp.gov/GPO/gpo1193304 zAddress at time of PURL creationuhttp://www.cdc.gov/spanish/niosh/docs/2013-149_sp/pdfs/2013-149_sp.pdf  aC0bGPO  abcb77 20190422b20190422  aPERM_INGEST_04282022  aPERM_INGE